{"uuid": "ea3afe8f-867e-46da-9bfd-84d9da5a127d", "id": 1913, "date": "2018-05-04T05:00:37", "date_gmt": "2018-05-04T12:00:37", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=1913"}, "modified": "2019-11-26T18:28:13", "modified_gmt": "2019-11-27T02:28:13", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-bobby-bandiera-under-the-boardwalk", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/05/04/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-bobby-bandiera-under-the-boardwalk/", "title": {"rendered": "Meeting Across the River: Bruce Springsteen and Bobby Bandiera, &#8220;Under the Boardwalk&#8221;"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Can anything scream &#8220;summer at the Jersey shore&#8221; more than Bruce Springsteen singing &#8220;Under the Boardwalk?&#8221; I\u00a0don&#8217;t think so.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s the first time Bruce played the The Drifters&#8217; 1964 classic, with Bobby Bandiera at The Stone Pony on June 24, 1989.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen with Bobby Bandiera - UNDER THE BOARDWALK 1989  (audio)\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/j0h8kVXEdX0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>&#8220;Under the Boardwalk&#8221; is a sequel of sorts to &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/12/15/cover-me-up-on-the-roof/\">Up on the Roof</a>,&#8221; another gorgeous Drifters song that Bruce has covered a few times (but we&#8217;ll cover that another day). Here&#8217;s the original, but you almost certainly know it&#8211;the opening notes played on bass, gourd, and triangle are instantly recognizable.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"The Drifters - Under the Boardwalk\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EPEqRMVnZNU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>Bruce covered &#8220;Under the Boardwalk&#8221; a few more times over the years. The last time was at a telethon for Hurricane Sandy relief&#8211;and it was a team-up as well, this time a bit more star-studded:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Jimmy Fallon, Steven Tyler, Billy Joel, &amp; Bruce Springsteen - Under the Boardwalk\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lPqDw4VtOJ4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>Under the Boardwalk<br />\nFirst performed:</strong> June 24, 1989 (Asbury Park, NJ)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> November 2, 2012 (New York City, NY)</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce and Bobby cover &#8220;Under the Boardwalk&#8221; on the Jersey Shore on the third day of summer. There&#8217;s no setting more perfect for that song.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 2008, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_